data.description: Welcome to this charming 2-family home nestled in the heart of Canarsie Brooklyn. This property offers a 2 bed | 1 bath over a 1 bed | 1 bath, full finished basement OSE with 2 rooms and a full bathroom. Enjoy the convenience of a front porch, spacious backyard ideal for outdoor gatherings and relaxation. Situated in a vibrant neighborhood, you'll have easy access to local shops, restaurants, and transportation options. Don't miss the opportunity to own this versatile and inviting 2-family house in the sought-after Brooklyn community with a 2 car driveway.
